# Part 3

## 1. Why are people keen on buying new electronic devices?

I think there are several reasons for that. First of all, technology develops very quickly nowadays, so new devices usually come with better performance, more advanced functions, and improved user experience. For example, newer smartphones often have better cameras, faster processors, and longer battery life, which naturally attract consumers.

Another reason is related to social influence and marketing. Many companies spend huge amounts of money on advertising, making people feel that they need the latest products to keep up with trends. In some cases, electronic devices have even become status symbols, especially among young people.

At the same time, people’s lifestyles are becoming increasingly digital, so electronic devices are no longer luxuries but necessities for study, work, and entertainment.

### 中文翻译：

我觉得原因有很多。首先，现在科技发展非常快，新设备通常拥有更强的性能、更先进的功能以及更好的使用体验。例如，新款手机通常会有更好的摄像头、更快的处理器以及更长的续航能力，所以自然会吸引消费者。

另一个原因和社会影响以及营销有关。很多公司会投入大量资金做广告，让人们觉得自己必须拥有最新产品才能跟上潮流。在某些情况下，电子产品甚至已经变成一种身份象征，尤其是在年轻人当中。

与此同时，人们的生活越来越数字化，所以电子设备已经不再是奢侈品，而是学习、工作和娱乐中的必需品。

